sform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-5\">Programa de Parceiros</p><h1 class=\"text-h1 font-heading font-medium text-white mb-5 leading-[1.05]\">Recomendas.<br/><span class=\"text-accent\">Ganhas 10%.</span><br/>Sempre.</h1><p class=\"text-muted text-base mb-9 max-w-[400px] leading-relaxed\">Cada cliente que nos trazes vale comissão real — sem limite, sem prazo, sem complicações.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4\"><a class=\"nova-btn font-body \" href=\"#aderir\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__glow\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__ring\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__shine\"></span><span class=\"nova-btn__label\">Tornar-me parceiro</span></a><a href=\"#como-funciona\" class=\"group inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-muted hover:text-white transition-colors\">Como funciona<svg class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 7h8M8 4l3 3-3 3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"flex justify-center lg:justify-end\"><div class=\"relative w-full max-w-[320px]\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -inset-10 rounded-full pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(52,211,153,0.16), transparent 65%)\"></div><div class=\"relative rounded-[28px] border p-7 shadow-[0_24px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)]\" style=\"border-color:rgba(52,211,153,0.22);background:linear-gradient(135deg, #0d1f18 0%, #091610 55%, #0F0F0E 100%)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-8\"><span class=\"relative flex size-2\"><span class=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-accent opacity-70\"></span><span class=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full size-2 bg-accent\"></span></span><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-accent/75\">Comissão confirmada</span></div><div class=\"text-[68px] font-heading font-medium leading-none tabular-nums mb-1\" style=\"color:#34d399\"><span>0<!-- -->€</span></div><p class=\"text-xs mb-7\" style=\"color:rgba(172,172,185,0.6)\">comissão · Projeto Website 1.500€</p><div class=\"w-full h-px mb-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(52,211,153,0.3), rgba(52,211,153,0.05), transparent)\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2.5\"><div class=\"flex justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs text-muted\">Parceiro</span><span class=\"text-xs font-medium\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)\">Ricardo J.</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs text-muted\">Taxa de comissão</span><span class=\"text-xs font-medium\" style=\"color:#34d399\">10%</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between\"><span class=\"text-xs text-muted\">Estado</span><span class=\"text-xs font-medium\" style=\"color:#34d399\">Pago ✓</span></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute -top-2 -right-2 size-9 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-black\" style=\"background:#34d399;box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(52,211,153,0.5)\">+</div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"como-funciona\" class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 scroll-mt-24\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"pt-24 pb-14 text-center\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-3\">O processo</p><h2 class=\"text-h2 font-heading font-medium text-white\">Três passos. Zero fricção.</h2></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 sm:gap-10 py-10 border-b border-white/[0.07]\"><div class=\"w-[44px] sm:w-[80px] flex-shrink-0 flex justify-end\"><span class=\"font-heading font-medium leading-none select-none\" style=\"font-size:clamp(56px, 7vw, 88px);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.045);letter-spacing:-0.04em\">01</span></div><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"width:5px;height:5px;background:rgba(52,211,153,0.38);box-shadow:none\"></div><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"font-heading font-medium text-white mb-2 leading-[1.15]\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 3vw, 32px);letter-spacing:-0.02em\">Recomendas</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-[520px]\">Apresentas um contacto à Element Group. Um email, uma mensagem, um nome — nós fazemos o resto da conversa.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0.12s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0.12s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 sm:gap-10 py-10 border-b border-white/[0.07]\"><div class=\"w-[44px] sm:w-[80px] flex-shrink-0 flex justify-end\"><span class=\"font-heading font-medium leading-none select-none\" style=\"font-size:clamp(56px, 7vw, 88px);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.045);letter-spacing:-0.04em\">02</span></div><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"width:5px;height:5px;background:rgba(52,211,153,0.38);box-shadow:none\"></div><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"font-heading font-medium text-white mb-2 leading-[1.15]\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 3vw, 32px);letter-spacing:-0.02em\">Fechamos</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-[520px]\">Apresentamos a proposta, acompanhamos o cliente e entregamos o projeto. Tu não precisas de estar envolvido.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0.24s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0.24s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 sm:gap-10 py-10 pb-24\"><div class=\"w-[44px] sm:w-[80px] flex-shrink-0 flex justify-end\"><span class=\"font-heading font-medium leading-none select-none\" style=\"font-size:clamp(56px, 7vw, 88px);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.045);letter-spacing:-0.04em\">03</span></div><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 rounded-full\" style=\"width:5px;height:5px;background:#34d399;box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(52,211,153,0.6)\"></div><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><h3 class=\"font-heading font-medium text-white mb-2 leading-[1.15]\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 3vw, 32px);letter-spacing:-0.02em\">Ganhas</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-[520px]\">Depois da entrega e pagamento, recebes 10% do valor do projeto diretamente no teu IBAN.</p></div><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 font-heading font-medium leading-none tabular-nums hidden sm:block\" style=\"font-size:clamp(48px, 6vw, 72px);color:#34d399;letter-spacing:-0.04em\"><span>0<!-- -->%</span></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 py-24 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-3 text-center\">Quanto podes ganhar</p><h2 class=\"text-h2 font-heading font-medium text-white text-center mb-4\">O teu ganho, a números reais.</h2><p class=\"text-muted text-sm text-center mb-12 max-w-[480px] mx-auto\">A comissão é sempre 10% do valor do projeto, paga após a entrega.</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);tr