balho.</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0.08s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0.08s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"rounded-[20px] p-6 h-full cursor-default\" style=\"background:#121212;border:1px solid;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);box-shadow:none;transition:background 0.28s, border-color 0.28s, box-shadow 0.28s\"><div class=\"rounded-full mb-6\" style=\"height:2px;width:28px;background:rgba(52,211,153,0.28);transition:width 0.32s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1), background 0.28s\"></div><div class=\"size-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4\" style=\"background:rgba(52,211,153,0.07);border:1px solid;border-color:rgba(52,211,153,0.15);color:#34d399;box-shadow:none;transition:background 0.28s, border-color 0.28s, box-shadow 0.28s\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"5\" width=\"14\" height=\"12\" rx=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\"></rect><path d=\"M3 9h14M7 3v4M13 3v4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-heading font-medium mb-2\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.82);transition:color 0.28s\">Contabilista / Consultor</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed\">Os teus clientes abrem empresas. Nós damos-lhes presença digital — tu ganhas por isso.</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0.16s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0.16s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"rounded-[20px] p-6 h-full cursor-default\" style=\"background:#121212;border:1px solid;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);box-shadow:none;transition:background 0.28s, border-color 0.28s, box-shadow 0.28s\"><div class=\"rounded-full mb-6\" style=\"height:2px;width:28px;background:rgba(52,211,153,0.28);transition:width 0.32s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1), background 0.28s\"></div><div class=\"size-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4\" style=\"background:rgba(52,211,153,0.07);border:1px solid;border-color:rgba(52,211,153,0.15);color:#34d399;box-shadow:none;transition:background 0.28s, border-color 0.28s, box-shadow 0.28s\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M10 2L2 7.5l8 5 8-5L10 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M2 13.5l8 5 8-5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-heading font-medium mb-2\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.82);transition:color 0.28s\">Agência Criativa</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed\">Subcontrata web ou amplia a oferta sem aumentar equipa. Comissão sobre cada projeto.</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0.24s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0.24s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"rounded-[20px] p-6 h-full cursor-default\" style=\"background:#121212;border:1px solid;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);box-shadow:none;transition:background 0.28s, border-color 0.28s, box-shadow 0.28s\"><div class=\"rounded-full mb-6\" style=\"height:2px;width:28px;background:rgba(52,211,153,0.28);transition:width 0.32s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1), background 0.28s\"></div><div class=\"size-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4\" style=\"background:rgba(52,211,153,0.07);border:1px solid;border-color:rgba(52,211,153,0.15);color:#34d399;box-shadow:none;transition:background 0.28s, border-color 0.28s, box-shadow 0.28s\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 5h14M3 10h14M3 15h8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-heading font-medium mb-2\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.82);transition:color 0.28s\">Formador / Mentor</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed\">A tua audiência precisa de ferramentas digitais. Liga-nos e ganha por cada referência.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 py-24 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[320px_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"rounded-[22px] p-7 lg:sticky lg:top-28\" style=\"background:#161616;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\"><div class=\"size-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-7\" style=\"background:#1e1e1e;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)\"><span class=\"font-heading font-semibold text-white text-sm tracking-tight\">E</span></div><p class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4\" style=\"color:rgba(52,211,153,0.6)\">FAQ</p><h2 class=\"font-heading font-medium text-white leading-[1.05] mb-4\" style=\"font-size:clamp(26px, 3vw, 36px);letter-spacing:-0.025em\">Ainda com<br/>dúvidas?</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-7\">Fala connosco sem compromisso. Respondemos em menos de 2 horas com tudo o que precisas de saber.</p><a href=\"#aderir\" class=\"inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium text-black transition-opacity hover:opacity-90\" style=\"background:#34d399\">Tornar-me parceiro</a><p class=\"text-[11px] mt-5\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.22)\">5.0 no Google · resposta em &lt; 2h</p></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0.1s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0.1s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"border-t pt-0\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\"><div><div class=\"border-b\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-6 py-5 text-left\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-colors duration-200\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.95)\">Como e quando recebo a comissão?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 text-xl leading-none font-light transition-colors duration-200\" style=\"color:#34d399\">−</span></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden\" style=\"height:auto;opacity:1\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 max-w-[560px]\">Após o projeto ser aceite e o primeiro pagamento processado, transferimos 10% do valor líquido para o teu IBAN em 10 dias úteis.</p></div></div><div class=\"border-b\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-6 py-5 text-left\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-colors duration-200\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72)\">O que conta como cliente válido?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 text-xl leading-none font-light transition-colors duration-200\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\">+</span></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden\" style=\"height:0px;opacity:0\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 max-w-[560px]\">Qualquer empresa ou profissional que contrate os nossos serviços por indicação direta tua — confirmada por email ou formulário de adesão.</p></div></div><div class=\"border-b\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-6 py-5 text-left\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-colors duration-200\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72)\">Há limite de comissões por mês?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 text-xl leading-none font-light transition-colors duration-200\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\">+</span></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden\" style=\"height:0px;opacity:0\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 max-w-[560px]\">Não. Podes referenciar quantos clientes quiseres. Cada projeto aprovado gera uma comissão independente.</p></div></div><div class=\"border-b\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-6 py-5 text-left\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-colors duration-200\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72)\">Preciso de emitir fatura?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 text-xl leading-none font-light transition-colors duration-200\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\">+</span></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden\" style=\"height:0px;opacity:0\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 max-w-[560px]\">Sim. Para transferências acima de 10€ pedimos recibo verde ou fatura pró-forma. Ajudamos no processo se necessário.</p></div></div><div class=\"border-b\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\"><button class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-6 py-5 text-left\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium leading-snug transition-colors duration-200\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72)\">E se o cliente cancelar o projeto?</span><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 text-xl leading-none font-light transition-colors duration-200\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\">+</span></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden\" style=\"height:0px;opacity:0\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed pb-5 max-w-[560px]\">A comissão é paga após o período de garantia de 14 dias. Cancelamentos antes desse prazo não geram comissão.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"aderir\" class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 py-24 px-6 scroll-mt-24\"><div class=\"max-w-[540px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-4 text-center\">Aderir ao programa</p><h2 class=\"text-h2 font-heading font-medium text-white mb-4 text-center\">Começa a ganhar<br/>hoje.</h2><p class=\"text-muted text-sm text-center mb-10 leading-relaxed\">Três passos rápidos. Entramos em contacto em 24h para confirmar os detalhes.</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden border\" style=\"border-color:rgba(52,211,153,0.14);background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(52,211,153,0.03) 0%, #111111 40%)\"><div class=\"flex gap-[3px] px-7 pt-7\"><div style=\"flex:1;height:3px;border-radius:9999px;background:#34d399;transition:background 0.35s ease\"></div><div style=\"flex:1;height:3px;border-radius:9999px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);transition:background 0.35s ease\"></div><div style=\"flex:1;height:3px;border-radius:9999px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);transition:background 0.35s ease\"></div><div style=\"flex:1;height:3px;border-radius:9999px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);transition:background 0.35s ease\"></div></div><div class=\"px-7 pt-6 pb-0\"><p class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-2\" style=\"color:rgba(52,211,153,0.55)\">Passo <!-- -->1<!-- --> de <!-- -->4<!-- --> — <!-- -->Sobre ti</p><h3 class=\"font-heading font-medium text-white leading-snug\" style=\"font-size:clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 22px)\">Quem és tu?</h3></div><div class=\"px-7 pt-6 pb-7\"><div style=\"display:block\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-3\"><div><label class=\"block text-xs text-muted mb-1.5\">Nome *</label><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"O teu nome\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder:text-white/25 focus:outline-none focus:border-accent/40 transition-colors\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"block text-xs text-muted mb-1.5\">Email *</label><input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"nome@empresa.pt\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder:text-white/25 focus:outline-none focus:border-accent/40 transition-colors\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div><label class=\"block text-xs text-muted mb-1.5\">Telefone <span class=\"text-white/25\">(opcional)</span></label><input type=\"tel\" placeholder=\"+351 9xx xxx xxx\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/10 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder:text-white/25 focus:outline-none focus:border-accent/40 transition-colors\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div style=\"display:none\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-xl border p-4 text-left transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02)\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)\">Designer / Criativo</span></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-xl border p-4 text-left transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02)\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)\">Consultor / Contabilista</span></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-xl border p-4 text-left transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02)\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)\">Agência Criativa</span></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-xl border p-4 text-left transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02)\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)\">Formador / Mentor</span></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-xl border p-4 text-left transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02)\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)\">Comercial / Vendas</span></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-xl border p-4 text-left transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02)\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)\">Outra área</span></button></div></div><div style=\"display:none\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-full border px-4 py-2 text-sm transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Clientes actuais</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-full border px-4 py-2 text-sm transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Redes sociais</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-full border px-4 py-2 text-sm transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Email / LinkedIn</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-full border px-4 py-2 text-sm transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Networking presencial</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-full border px-4 py-2 text-sm transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Comunidade online</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"rounded-full border px-4 py-2 text-sm transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\">Outro</button></div></div><div style=\"display:none\"><div class=\"mb-5\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 py-2.5 border-b\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\"><span class=\"text-xs flex-shrink-0\" style=\"color:rgba(172,172,185,0.45)\">Nome</span><span class=\"text-xs text-right\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75)\"></span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 py-2.5 border-b\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\"><span class=\"text-xs flex-shrink-0\" style=\"color:rgba(172,172,185,0.45)\">Email</span><span class=\"text-xs text-right\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75)\"></span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 py-2.5 border-b\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\"><span class=\"text-xs flex-shrink-0\" style=\"color:rgba(172,172,185,0.45)\">Telefone</span><span class=\"text-xs text-right\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75)\">—</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 py-2.5 border-b\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\"><span class=\"text-xs flex-shrink-0\" style=\"color:rgba(172,172,185,0.45)\">Perfil</span><span class=\"text-xs text-right\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75)\">—</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-4 py-2.5 border-b\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\"><span class=\"text-xs flex-shrink-0\" style=\"color:rgba(172,172,185,0.45)\">Canais</span><span class=\"text-xs text-right\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75)\">—</span></div></div><label class=\"flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer mb-5 select-none\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 size-4 rounded border flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-200\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);background:transparent;cursor:pointer\"></div><span class=\"text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed\">Aceito os termos do Programa de Parceiros e autorizo o contacto da Element Group para confirmação da minha adesão.</span></label></div><div class=\"flex gap-2 mt-6 justify-end\"><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-all d